item.title: PSDevCon 2023: Do you speak PrestaShop?
item.description: Do you speak PrestaShop? On November 30, Nicolas Lœuillet and Julie Varisellaz gave a presentation about the project’s translations at the first-ever PrestaShop Developer Conference.
